FBIS4-38848 "drsov107_b_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Edict Declares 12 Jun National Holiday Yeltsin Edict Declares 12 Jun National Holiday LD0206162494 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1559 GMT 2 Jun 94 LD0206162494 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow June 2 TASS -- President Boris Yeltsin of Russia has issued a decree, under which June 12 -- the day when the declaration on state sovereignty of the Russian Federation was passed in 1991 -- will be a national holiday. The press service of the Russian president circulated the news on Thursday.
